            "url": "https://kimiquotes.pages.dev/api"
          }
        ],
        "title": "Kimi Quotes API",
        "version": "1.0.0",
        "tagline": "Random and bulk quotes from Formula 1 driver Kimi Raikkonen, including team radio snippets and interview lines",
        "homepage": "https://kimiquotes.pages.dev/api",
        "docs_url": "https://freepublicapis.com/kimi-quotes-api",
        "about_md": "The Kimi Quotes API is a small, free, no-auth service that returns quotes attributed to Finnish Formula 1 driver Kimi Raikkonen, drawn from team radio exchanges and press interviews. It is hosted on Cloudflare Pages at [kimiquotes.pages.dev](https://kimiquotes.pages.dev/api).\n\nWhat you get from the API:\n- A random quote on demand\n- The full collection of quotes in a single call\n\nThe service is public and unauthenticated. CORS is disabled on the endpoints, so calls are best made from a server or proxy rather than directly from a browser. No published rate limits, licence terms, or attribution requirements were found at the time of writing.",
        "entity_desc": {
          "quote": "A single Kimi Raikkonen utterance; fetch one at random via `GET /api/quote` or the whole list via `GET /api/quotes`."
        },
